OL,3,CHeart attack patients told to make own
OL,4,Cway to hospital
OL,6,FThe Ambulance Service is having to
OL,7,Fadvise some heart-attack and stroke
OL,8,Fpatients to make their own way to
OL,9,Fhospital or face waiting several hours
OL,10,Ffor an ambulance.
OL,12,FIt comes as the health system in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland continues to face
OL,14,Fimmense pressures.
OL,16,FWith a third of crews stuck outside
OL,17,Femergency departments on Friday
OL,18,Fmorning, staff in ambulance control
OL,19,Fare having to prioritise which patient
OL,20,Fgets the next free ambulance.
