OL,3,CHeart attack patients told to make own
OL,4,Cway to hospital
OL,6,FThe head of the Ambulance Service, Dr
OL,7,FNigel Ruddell, said long delays mean
OL,8,Fseriously ill patients are being asked
OL,9,Fto make their own way to A&E.
OL,11,F"Sometimes the risk of waiting what is
OL,12,Fgoing to be a significant period for
OL,13,Fan ambulance might be greater than
OL,14,Fputting somebody in a car and
OL,15,Ftransporting them to hospital," he
OL,16,Ftold UTV.
OL,18,F"Even in some more serious
OL,19,Femergencies."
