OL,3,CHeart attack patients told to make own
OL,4,Cway to hospital
OL,6,FDr Ruddell said a backlog of
OL,7,Fambulances outside emergency
OL,8,Fdepartments across Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fhas been leading to delays in response
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,12,FOn Friday morning, one patient had
OL,13,Fbeen waiting 18 hours at home for an
OL,14,Fambulance while another waited 12
OL,15,Fhours in an ambulance outside of an
OL,16,Femergency department.
