OL,3,CHeart attack patients told to make own
OL,4,Cway to hospital
OL,6,F"We do know there's lots of evidence
OL,7,Fto show patients who have a delayed
OL,8,Fresponse are at increased risk of
OL,9,Fharm, both waiting for an ambulance
OL,10,Fresponse and waiting outside emergency
OL,11,Fdepartments to be properly admitted to
OL,12,Fhospital and to start their definitive
OL,13,Fcare," he continued.
OL,15,F"Yes there's no doubt that the longer
OL,16,Fthose delays happen there is increased
OL,17,Frisk of serious harm and death."
